# Task: Multi-Constraint Check (Density 13)
# Interface:
Class: Solution
Method: isValid(self, n: int) -> bool

# Objective:
Return True if the integer `n` satisfies ALL of the following 13 independent constraints:
1. n is greater than 2
2. n is not equal to 104
3. n is a multiple of 1
4. n is greater than 8
5. n is not equal to 110
6. n is a multiple of 2
7. n is greater than 14
8. n is not equal to 116
9. n is a multiple of 4
10. n is greater than 20
11. n is not equal to 122
12. n is a multiple of 5
13. n is greater than 26

class Solution:
    def isValid(self, n: int) -> bool:
        constraints = [
            n > 2,
            n != 104,
            n % 1 == 0,
            n > 8,
            n != 110,
            n % 2 == 0,
            n > 14,
            n != 116,
            n % 4 == 0,
            n > 20,
            n != 122,
            n % 5 == 0,
            n > 26
        ]
        return all(constraints)
